State.Description: Hand to Hand is an addon for Adamant - A Perk Overhaul that merges Lockpicking and Pickpocketing into a single skill and adds a new perk tree for Hand to Hand combat.
State.Name: Hand to Hand - An Adamant Addon

State.Author: ecirbaf
State.Description: Ever pick the wrong item in a dialogue with a NPC? This mod aims to fix some annoyances with the way keyboard and mouse selection works in the dialogue interface.
State.Name: Better Dialogue Controls

State.Author: doodlum
State.Description: dTry's SKSE plugins ported to 1.6.640/NG in a FOMOD installer. Includes Key Utils, Combat Music Fix, Stop On Slash, Shield Of Stamina, No Crime Teleport RE, Elden Parry, Elden Counter.
State.Name: dTry Plugin Updates

State.Author: colinswrath
State.Description: This is a simple SKSE plugin implementation similar to "First Person Camera Height Fix" or other mods.
State.Name: First Person Height Fix SKSE

State.Author: epinter
State.Description: Fixes media keys (volume, play/next/mute, windows key, alt+f4, etc...) by removing game's exclusive access to the keyboard. There's an option to fix deadkeys bug, and to enable Windows key.
State.Name: Media Keys Fix SKSE

State.Author: SlavicPotato
State.Description: All-in-one solution for smooth FPS-unlocked gameplay. Includes a physics fix, borderless fullscreen performance boost, refresh rate control, highly configurable frame rate limiting, various bugfixes and more.
State.Name: SSE Display Tweaks

Original.Name: Adamant - Bard Perks Addon - Pilgrim Integration-30191-1-1-0-1702183343.7z

State.Author: SimonMagus
State.Description: Adamant is a complete overhaul of Skyrim’s perk trees designed to balance existing skills and add powerful new perks to the game.
State.Name: Adamant - A Perk Overhaul

State.Author: Simon Magus - DeltaRider - Oreo
State.Description: Artificer is a complete overhaul of Skyrim's artifacts, designed to distribute Thaumaturgy and Mysticism enchantments throughout the game while ensuring that non-crafting characters can find powerful weapons and armor through questing.
State.Name: Artificer - An Artifact Overhaul

State.Author: ecirbaf
State.Description: Navigate all message boxes with the Left/Right and Activate (E) keys. Also fixes the clickable area of buttons so they are easier to select with the mouse.
State.Name: Better MessageBox Controls

State.Author: Ersh
State.Description: Fixes the queue getting overloaded when a lot of animations are queued for loading at the same time
State.Name: Animation Queue Fix

State.Author: Catir
State.Description: Tweaks True HUD's boss bar feature to be much stricter in its selection, reserving boss bars for bosses that are important to the story or have unique mechanics. Includes full Creation Club support and support for several quest mods.
State.Name: Curated Bosses for True HUD
